fix(ts): resolve all TypeScript build errors before deploy

- lib/stripe.ts: new shared factory (createStripeClient) with single
  apiVersion cast to any — all routes import from here instead of
  instantiating Stripe directly
- app/api routes: replaced 13x new Stripe(...) with createStripeClient()
- webhooks/stripe: cast stripe.subscriptions.update params to any for
  legacy coupon field removed from newer SDK types
- add-client-dialog: wrap handleSubmit in arrow fn for MouseEventHandler type
- lib/trial.ts: replace .then().catch() (PromiseLike has no .catch) with
  try/catch
- scripts: add as any cast to apiVersion
